column1: # Definition: Share of females that are employers. Employers are those workers who, working on their own account or with one or a few partners, hold the type of jobs defined as a “self-employment jobs”.
# Source: International Labour Organization (ILO) Key Indicators of the Labour Market (KILM)
# Data from the No Ceilings project: http://noceilings.org
# For more about the data, please visit http://noceilings.org/data
